## Column Label Options

To enable column labels, set the `enabled` property in `label` options as shown:

```js
sparklineOptions: {
    type: 'bar',
    direction: 'vertical',
    label: {
        enabled: true // show column labels
    }
}
```

{% flex justifyContent="center" %}
{% imageCaption imagePath="resources/default.png" alt="Column default" constrained=true width="250px" enableDarkModeFilter=true %}
Default
{% /imageCaption %}
{% imageCaption imagePath="resources/default-label.png" alt="Column labels enabled" constrained=true width="250px" enableDarkModeFilter=true %}
